		{
			"id": "69a4634c-bdc7-4280-8924-9482aadbc1e5",
			"name": "69a4634c-bdc7-4280-8924-9482aadbc1e5",
			"type": "facts",
			"content": {
				"number": "1",
				"title": "Hypertensiv kris och malign hypertoni",
				"text": "<table class=\"table table-bordered facts\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Symtom<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Huvudv&auml;rk, yrsel, illam&aring;ende, andn&ouml;d, medvetanderubbning, synst&ouml;rning</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Kliniska fynd</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&Ouml;gonbottenf&ouml;r&auml;ndringar obligat vid malign hypertoni, bl&ouml;dningar och/eller papill&ouml;dem (fundus hypertonikus 3, 4)</li>\r\n<li>Blodtryck vanligen mycket h&ouml;gt &gt;&nbsp;240/&gt;&nbsp;120 mm&nbsp;Hg</li>\r\n<li>V&auml;nsterkammarhypertrofi p&aring; EKG, hj&auml;rtsvikt/lung&ouml;dem</li>\r\n<li>Proteinuri, kreatininf&ouml;rh&ouml;jning</li>\r\n<li>L&aring;gt P-kalium (prim&auml;r eller sekund&auml;r hyperaldosteronism)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Differentialdiagnoser</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Blodtrycksf&ouml;rh&ouml;jning vid akut stroke (bilddiagnostik av hj&auml;rnan)</li>\r\n<li>Intoxikation eller abstinens</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><strong>Behandling<br /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Inneliggande p&aring; sjukhus, se Tabell xx</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
